# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo AND on checkout, so Windows core.autocrlf
# does not rewrite line endings to CRLF and fight Prettier (endOfLine: "lf") + ESLint.
# This removes the recurring "Delete ␍ (prettier/prettier)" false errors in the IDE.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files — never touch line endings.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
